  "title": "Hits widget: transformData not always called when refining",
  "body": "When using a `refinementList` (or presumably other sorts of filtering), if a hit exists before and after refinement, `transformData` is NOT called the subsequent time(s).\n\nOriginal post: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/37924976/instantsearch-js-hits-widget-transforming-data-on-refinement?noredirect=1#comment63313526_37924976\n\nDemo: https://jsfiddle.net/timkelty/LyuL5eze/7/\n",
